name: SACRIFICE
description:
The roots of sacrifice go back to very distant times.
Paganism, deities, altars.
But throughout the entire time, 
one detail was present in the issue of sacrifice - people.

Humans are the only creatures capable of maintaining friendly relations with their victims, which they intend to eat, before they are eaten.

Even among themselves.


:: visuals: @cryptohamster | sound-design: @bisdvrk
